    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277680</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_020_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんか、肌寒いし、
歩きづらいし……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the... It's freezing here. It's hard to walk...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>277908</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_020_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……マジ、この道、
合ってんのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is this...where the paths meet?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_020_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>くんくん……
風の匂いが
こっちからするし……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>*sniff* There is something smelly in the air...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278168</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_020_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ははっ、
&lt;Mel&gt;、ブタっぽい顔に
なってんぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hah! &lt;Mel&gt;, you can tell us if you just let one go...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_020_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いちち……
大体、風の匂いって
どんなだよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ouch! Ugh, anyways, what did you
mean by something smelly in the air?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_020_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>風の匂いはわかんないけど、
ジメジメがないのは、空気が
抜けてるから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't know about the smell you're talking about, 
considering it's pretty dry and the heavy atmosphere
should have removed any trace of it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278476</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_020_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>このまま進めば、
外出られるね、きっと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But I'm sure if we keep going, we
should be able to find the exit! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278576</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_020_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;……
やっぱり君の目的は
ダオスなのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Rody...your real reason to be here is Dhaos, am I right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>278860</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_020_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>人の目的なんて
そう簡単に変わんないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>People's motives don't change that easily...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_020_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でもダオスって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But Dhaos is...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>279168</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_060_020_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ま、私のことで
時間潰すなんてムダだよね。
ほら、行こ行こ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh dear, look how much time we've
been wasting! C'mon, let's move! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
